{"tid":1570393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《孫子兵法》兵無常勢，水無常形","createTime":"2019-09-15T05:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T07:00:43.000Z","uid":299387,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6d4db81cd73f8e3a49f287be4b63aaea3b1be935","tid":1570393,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"毅進仔讀唔成書所以做狗，所以各位手足作戰之餘都請多d閱讀好好充實自己，比d心機練體能，文武雙全先係最型。<br />\n<br />\n經過尋日淘大一役，真心希望各位唔好比所謂「角色」限制自己，勇武都識智取，和理都應該要識保護自己，與其互相指罵，不如諗下點樣可以將自己既功能發揮得最好。<br />\n<br />\n連登係呢埋運動中咁成功，就係因為有文有武既手足互相配合。<br />\n當對家改變策略，我地呢邊都應該好好部署下，重整旗鼓。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>兵無常勢，水無常形，能因敵變化而取勝者，謂之神。</strong><br />\n<br />\n大家可以參考下《孫子兵法》，集思廣益。《孫子兵法》由春秋時期孫武所作，係兵家最早既一部兵書，亦都係兵書戰策既鼻祖之作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，個人絕對認同「勇武」（你我個username都知），見到勇武手足不斷進步真心覺得你地好型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但要記住，「不戰而屈人之兵」，作戰唔應該以捨身救國為目標，係要諗辦法用最少既代價換取對方最大既傷害。"},{"pid":"96dd90069edf44bd3d99590e43281bee14154426","tid":1570393,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:32:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41243183ecc9bbb406891b301d21200e4eb28b3f","tid":1570393,"uid":145225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:32:04.000Z","msg":"好post冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24da32f6cfd048f67e33d13d4ae94ef25f23efc1","tid":1570393,"uid":20820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"推，孫子應該想彈返起身鬧我地"},{"pid":"4ad9326491c2e2c26abd56669825a27de8e02230","tid":1570393,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動係咪壽終正寢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563531</a><br />\n<br />\n要抵制人民日報廢嗡，我哋需要有相應嘅評論文章<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570306</a><br />\n<br />\n［熱門唔該］冇人講監控燈柱查到啲咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560935</a><br />\n<br />\n[學術研究]水馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1336880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1336880</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非奇招: 寄信輸出革命2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528683</a><br />\n<br />\n其實有冇善良嘅黑社會？即係企喺我哋依邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1520306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1520306</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇人想喺狗隻招募日做現場宣傳？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380083</a>"},{"pid":"8253906b090243b29e9c0495bc2612dd3d8aa43f","tid":1570393,"uid":295471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c16b13ef02bb942afad6d09895f231e2a8f6c6","tid":1570393,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25204ba72c7b8d5f36a2df90dd1b06f786279e8","tid":1570393,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0f4707486041f63327117852de036a5c57eaf0","tid":1570393,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"2點半銅鑼灣東角道<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" c